name: gulp-ng-html2js
description: a gulp plugin which generates angularjs modules, which pre-load your html code into the $templatecache. this way angularjs doesn't need to request the actual html files anymore.
kwds: a gulp plugin which generates angularjs modules, which pre-load your html code into the $templatecache. this way angularjs doesn't need to request the actual html files anymore. gulpplugin ng-html2js angular html2js angularjs
